<p source="SHANGBO.LINGWANGSUISHEN 9.55.1 (STRIP 1) MACHENGYUAN 9: 158 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-1a.1">靈王既位，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-1a.2">申息不慭[=寧].</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-1a.3">王敗蔡靈侯於呂，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-1a.4">命申人室[=實]出，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-1a.5">取蔡之器.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LINGWANGSUISHEN 9.55.2 (STRIPS 1-2 ) MACHENGYUAN 9: 158-160 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-2a.1">執事人夾蔡人之軍門，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-2a.2">命人毋 [1] 敢徒[=空]出.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-2a.3">申成公識其子虛未蓄髮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-2a.4">命之遣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-2a.5">虛三徒出,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-2a.6">執事人止之.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LINGWANGSUISHEN 9.55.3 (STRIPS 2-3) MACHENGYUAN 9: 160-161 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-3a.1">虛乘一輚駟,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-3a.2">告執事人 [2]:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-3a.3">“小人幼,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-3a.4">不能以施器.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-3a.5">得此車,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-3a.6">或不能御之以歸.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LINGWANGSUISHEN 9.55.4 (STRIPS 3-4) MACHENGYUAN 9: 161-162 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-4a.1">命以其策歸.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-4a.2">執事人許之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-4a.3">虛秉策以歸 [3],</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-4a.4">至擊澨,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-4a.5">又棄其策焉.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LINGWANGSUISHEN 9.55.5 (STRIPS 4-5) MACHENGYUAN 9: 162-164 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-5a.1">成公懼其又取焉，Duke Ceng feared that he would have to (go back and) take (some weapon) again (?),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-5a.2">而諄[or 逆?]之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-5a.3">諒爲之怒：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-5a.4">“舉邦盡獲，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-5a.5">汝獨亡[4] 得！”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-5a.6">虛不答.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-5a.7">又爲之怒.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LINGWANGSUISHEN 9.55.6 (STRIP 5) MACHENGYUAN 9: 164 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-6a.1">虛答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-6a.2">“君爲王臣，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-6a.3">王將墜邦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-6a.4">弗能止,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-6a.5">而又欲得焉?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-6a.6">成公與虛歸,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0083_tls_001-6a.7">爲落.[5]</seg></p>

